Class ListenerInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.configuration.ListenerInfo

  • public class ListenerInfo
extends Object
    A utility class that stores some information pertaining to a Listener. This object is referred used by ListenerManager.registerListener(ListenerInfo).
